161
00:21:19,545 --> 00:21:21,185
Yao Baiyuan fell to his death.

162
00:21:21,265 --> 00:21:22,705
Wu Shanlong fell to his death.

163
00:21:22,785 --> 00:21:23,985
Uncle Ran had a car accident.

164
00:21:24,625 --> 00:21:26,865
There was construction at every scene,
and there was grease at every scene.

165
00:21:27,905 --> 00:21:29,225
