they died in accidents?

168
00:21:38,825 --> 00:21:41,185
Wu Shanlong was. Yao Baiyuan wasn't.

169
00:21:42,505 --> 00:21:43,625
Yao Baiyuan…

170
00:21:48,065 --> 00:21:49,185
Ran…

171
