175
00:22:10,505 --> 00:22:11,865
It was her.

176
00:22:14,185 --> 00:22:15,425
It was her.

177
00:22:16,505 --> 00:22:18,465
She was the one who killed Ran.

178
00:22:25,545 --> 00:22:26,505
Who?

179
00:22:27,625 --> 00:22:29,265
Who killed Uncle Ran?

180
00:22:38,745 --> 00:22:39,585
Xu Meng.

181
00:22:41,585 --> 00:22:42,705
It was Xu Meng.

182
00:22:44,545 --> 00:22:46,025
Xu Meng didn't die.

183
00:22:48,865 --> 00:22:50,545
She's been alive all along.

184
00:24:24,265 --> 00:24:25,105
